Summary: Star shaped moving at very high rate of speed at high altitude
trends: There have been 52 other sightings in Minneapolis
There were no other sightings in Minneapolis on or around May 21st 2010
divs: Sighting DetailsAt 11:29 I was outside smoking a cigarette when I noticed what appeared to be a meteor entering our atmosphere. It was moving from East to West. Approx. 2 minutes after a Star Shaped object appered from the North moving at an extremly high speed at an altitude that was exceedingly higher than any commerical aircraft would fly. The Star shaped object was in sight for approx 8-10 seconds until the object went black and disapeared approximately where the meteor entered the atmosphere. the sky was perfectly clear with no cloud cover.
